199
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,400
Aren't you the one from that day—

200
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,360
The young lady praying for a child.

201
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,640
Oh, it's you, sister.

202
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,040
