00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:45,480
Why is it only your shop that can sell it?

293
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:46,680
You don't get it, do you?

294
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,680
The petals of the Night Begonia

295
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:50,800
are dark purple.

296
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:53,040
In the trade, it's called "black gold."

297
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,360
Not only that,

298
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,920
it gives off a unique fragrance.

299
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,680
Ladies of high status often use it as a spice.

300
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,240
The amazing thing is,

301
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,920
once it touches alcohol, it becomes colorless and tasteless.

302
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,600
It also becomes highly poisonous.

303
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:09,040
If someone accidentally drinks it,

304
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,480
it could be fatal.

305
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,160
Boss

306
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,240
You say that,

307
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,440
how do I know if it's true?

308
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,040
If it really is poisonous,

309
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,480
why would anyone buy it?

310
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,600
You don't know, do you?

311
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:24,560
But people actually do buy it.

312
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:25,240
And

313
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,360
they pay a pretty high price for it.

314
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:27,360
Of course,

315
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:28,800
as for me,

316
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:31,360
every time I sell some, I remind them repeatedly.

317
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,680
As for them,

318
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,240
when they buy it,

319
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,120
they just put it in a sachet and smell it, that's all.

320
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,040
I don't believe that.

321
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:40,480
You've been talking for so long, but I haven't seen anything.

322
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,360
How do we know if it's real or fake?

323
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:42,600
Yeah,

324
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,120
right?

325
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,360
If you don't believe me,

326
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,600
I'll show it to you.

327
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,040
Grind it well.

328
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,600
Buddy,

329
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,160
what kind of medicine is this?

330
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,160
This is Darjeeling tea.

331
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:00,680
And what about this one?

332
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,600
It's the stamen of a balloon flower.

333
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:07,680
Go ahead, keep busy.

334
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,120
No.
